        "message": "=<h2>Aureon AI Daily Job Report</h2>\n\n<p><strong>Job Title:</strong><br>\n{{ $('AI Agent').item.json.output[\"Job Title\"] }}\n</p>\n<p><strong>Company:</strong><br>\n{{ $('AI Agent').item.json.output[\"Company\"] }}\n</p>\n\n<p><strong>Match Score:</strong><br>\n{{ $('AI Agent').item.json.output[\"Match Score\"] }}\n</p>\n\n<p><strong>Recommendation:</strong><br>\n{{ $('AI Agent').item.json.output[\"Recommendation\"] }}\n</p>\n\n<p><strong>Reason:</strong><br>\n{{ $('AI Agent').item.json.output[\"Reason\"] }}\n</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<h3>Generated Application</h3>\n\n<p><strong>Proposal Subject:</strong><br>\n{{ $('AI Agent').item.json.output[\"Proposal Subject\"] }}\n</p>\n\n<p><strong>Cover Letter:</strong><br>\n{{ $('AI Agent').item.json.output[\"Proposal\"] }}\n</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p><strong>Job Link:</strong><br>\n<a href=\"{{ $('AI Agent').item.json.output[\"Job Link\"] }}\">Open Job Opportunity</a>\n</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p><em>This report was generated automatically by the Aureon AI Job Search & Proposal Assistant.</em></p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>This email was sent automatically with n8n.</p>",
